Unable to give this a rating as it was given as a gift and was not for myself.
It's one of James Woods better films....He's very much like Rudy....very believable.....a really GOOD film....The actress playing his wife was really good too.

What I do notv like is that the dvds are put in one socket. It is a great deal. It does not have a documentary on those days events put together in one dvd. I am not putting the item down it is good but if you want do learn about the entire  days events buy inside 9/11.

This is an excellent DVD, and I would recommend it to anyone.  I believe we should always remember 911, and this DVD is a must- have for anyone's video library.  It is a gripping reminder of the extent of the tragedy of that terrible day.
